Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:47.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,((ヨタ：デコ　デコ　デコ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:50.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,（サクラ）もう！\N人が気にしてることを！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:55.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,わぁ！\Nゴッツンコ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:58.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:00.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:03.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,♪♪「コン　コン　コン　雪がコン」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:05.68,japanese,,0,0,0,,（シカマル）ヨタに\N気に入られたみたいだな　お前。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:07.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,（いの）おでこがね！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:12.18,japanese,,0,0,0,,ピッタンコ！\Nあなた…　何なの！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:16.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,♪♪「コン　コン　コン　コン　コン　コン」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:20.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,「コン　コン　コン」って…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:55.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,あぁ…　せっかくお家から\Nくすねた花束渡そうとしたらね→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:59.18,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケ君　プイッて\N無視して行っちゃったんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:03.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,フフフ…　悲しいな。\Nいのが　かわいそう。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:06.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,かわいそうにね　いの。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:11.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,優しいんだね　あげる。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:15.18,japanese,,0,0,0,,《いのちゃん　積極的なんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:17.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケ君に　そんなこと…》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:20.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,楽しいの？　サクラ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:23.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,えっ？\Nサクラが楽しいとヨタも楽しい。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:26.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,サクラ　何が楽しいのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:28.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,あっ…　違うの　いのちゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:30.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,キャハハハ　ハハハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:32.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,ムーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:36.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,（チョウジ）ヨタは　お天気屋だね。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:41.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,悲しけりゃ雨が降る。\N楽しけりゃ雪が降る　か…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:45.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,んっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:05.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,んっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:07.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,（いの）あの花…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:09.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,（シカマル）ヨタが？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,里に？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:18.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,（チョウジ）もうダメだよ　ヨタ。\Nお前は里には秘密なんだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:21.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,見つかったら大変なことに\Nなっちゃうんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:23.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,誰にも見られてないだろうな。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:27.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,うん　私\N誰にも見られてない！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:29.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,ホントか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:32.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,１人　変な子がいた。\N誰！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:37.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,みんなが　お昼ごはん食べてるとき\N１人だけお外に出てて→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:39.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,鉄棒に座ってたよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:42.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,鉄棒？　ナルトか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:51.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,う～ん　もしかして　あの子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:04.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,あっ　いるいる！\Nいつも１人で　なんか怒ってる！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:09.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,そう？　私には　なんか\Nニヤけた顔して見てくる。　変なヤツ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:14.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,アンタに気があんじゃないの？\Nえっ！？　やめて。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルトは　お前に気づいたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:19.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,たぶん…　知らない。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:23.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,あのね　ヨタ。\Nもう絶対　里に行っちゃダメだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:25.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,見つかったら　私たち→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:28.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,離れ離れになっちゃうかも\Nしれないんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:32.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,私　やだよ！\Nサクラと離れたくないよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:35.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,サクラだけなの？\Nありがとう　ヨタ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:39.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,でも　おもしろかったね　サスケ君。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:44.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,(いつも　クールなのに…\Nフフフッ　お花畑みたいだった))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:14.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,くっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:21.31,japanese,,0,0,0,,やっぱり　ヨタと\N戦うことになっちゃうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:26.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,アスマのときのように\N封印するため…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:28.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,うっ…　戦うしか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:33.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,でも　どうやって…\Nヨタのお天気に　僕たち勝てるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,知るかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:37.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,（みんな）うわ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:41.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,《考えてみたら\N俺たち　なんにも→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:44.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタのこと知らねえんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:47.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,どうやったら…》
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:51.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,《父さん　サクラにつなげて！》
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:54.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,（いのいち）わかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:56.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,サクラ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,《いの：サクラ…　聞こえる？》
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:02.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,《いの…　ごめん。\Nちょっと取り込んでる》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:05.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,《アンタ　覚えてない？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:08.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,覚えてるでしょ？　ヨタのこと！》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:13.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ちょ…　ちょっと待って。\N今　そのヨタが目の前に…》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:17.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,どういうこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,《キバ：俺んところもだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:28.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,キバ：ヨタのヤツ　すんげぇ怒ってる》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:30.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,なに！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:36.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,《て　なんで　お前たちんとこにも\Nヨタがいるんだよ？》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:39.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ヨタが…　３人も》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:43.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,いったい　どうなってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:58.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,（ナルト）口笛…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:16.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前…　誰だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:21.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:29.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,え…　あっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:32.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:35.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前　ヨタ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:37.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,ハハッ！\Nヨタなのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:45.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,((なんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:15.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,ちょっと　アンタね　ヨタをどこに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:21.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,探り探りで聞くのは難しいな…\Nナルト　お前　知ってるよな？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:23.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,何を？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:26.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,う～ん…　何か見ただろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:29.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,見かけねえような…　その…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:32.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,見かけねえのを\Nどうやって見るんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:36.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前　意外と頭いいな。\Nうん　うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:39.45,japanese,,0,0,0,,ちょっと　アンタたち\Nなに感心してんのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:42.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,ちょっと…　来て！\Nちょっ…　何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:52.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,あ…。\Nヨタを　どこへやったのよ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:54.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,え…　ヨタ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:57.85,japanese,,0,0,0,,（サクラ）この前\Nアカデミーの校庭で会ったんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:10:04.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタを知ってるのは　私たちの他は\Nあなただけなんだから！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:17.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,アンタ！　ヨタに会ったんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:20.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,みんなに\Nばらしちゃったんでしょ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:22.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタって　誰なんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:24.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,里の近くで迷子になってたのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:27.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,かわいそうだから\N私たちが面倒をみてさ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:31.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,それが　今日　ここに来てみたら\Nめちゃくちゃで→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:33.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタも　いないんだもん！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:36.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　ソイツってば\Nよそ者じゃねえかよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:38.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:43.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんで　よそ者のヤツは　かばって…\N俺には　そんな目をしやがんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:47.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,ちょっと…　何よ！？　その言い方！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:53.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,生意気ね！\Nう～ん…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:57.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,って…　証拠も何もねえのに\N問い詰めすぎたかな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:02.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,もし　本当に\N何も知らなかったら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:13.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,チクショウ！\Nなんで　いつも　俺ばっか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:24.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,迷った…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:41.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,(お前…))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:58.64,japanese,,0,0,0,,((あっ！　もしかして…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:07.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,ゲッ！　な…　なんなんだよ！？　お前。\Nどうしたんだってばよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:13.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,どうしたんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:16.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,私…　怖いよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,私って…　何？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,私は　ヨタだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:23.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,えっ！？　やっぱ　お前がヨタか！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:26.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,うわ～ん！\Nギャーッ！　痛い　痛い…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:34.64,japanese,,0,0,0,,お天気雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:38.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,これって　もしかして　お前の術？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:43.98,japanese,,0,0,0,,いいな…　俺なんか　分身の術も\N変化の術もできなくって→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:47.98,japanese,,0,0,0,,いつも　イルカティーチャーに\N怒られてばっかで…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:54.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,よそ者のくせに\Nみんなに好かれてよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:58.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,俺ってば…。\Nあ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:01.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,私　知ってるよ　お前。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:04.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,フーッ　フーッ　フーッて。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:06.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,ん？\Nこの前　鉄棒に座って→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:09.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,口で笛吹いてた。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:11.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,あ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:42.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,教えて　私も口で笛吹きたい。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:44.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,は？\Nだって　アンタ笛吹いたら→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:47.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,１人じゃなくなってた。\N元気出てた。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:53.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,出てねえよ。　口笛で\Nごまかしてただけだってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:56.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　ヨタもごまかしてみる。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:58.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,だって　お前には　みんながいて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:10.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:29.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,教えておくれよ　私にも口笛。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:31.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,ああ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:40.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,見てろよ　ここ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:43.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,はじめは\Nとんがらせないで息を出すんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:45.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,で　だんだん狭くする。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:47.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,風の音を出すんだ　ひゅ～って。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:49.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,《コイツ　喜んでやがる。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:01.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,喜びが風になるのか》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:08.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,ねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:13.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:20.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,友達。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:23.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,友達だってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:27.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,（２人）アハハハッ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:40.45,japanese,,0,0,0,,（キバ）あ　いやがった　この野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:43.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,待て　コラ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:48.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヤダ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:56.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,コイツ　また。\Nヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,私　犬嫌い！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:04.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前ら　ヨタに何したんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:09.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,知らねえよ。　赤丸と\N散歩してたら　ヤツに会って…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:13.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,したら　雷が　バンバン落ちてきて。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:15.45,japanese,,0,0,0,,コイツの仕業だろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:18.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,うわ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:21.98,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！\Nあっ　あの子！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:24.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,キャー！\Nヨタ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:26.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,プン　プン　プン。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:30.48,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタのヤツ　怒ると雷かよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:50.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,それ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:52.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,（みんな）わ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:56.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,よしよし。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:13.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,い～ち　に～　さ～ん→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:19.45,japanese,,0,0,0,,し～　ご～　ろ～く　な～な→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:23.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,は～ち　きゅ～う　とお。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:26.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,じゅ～いち　じゅ～に→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:30.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,じゅ～さん　じゅ～し…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:33.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,私もナルトと一緒！\Nバカ　ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:35.45,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前がいると　すぐわかっちまう。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:37.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,キュフフフ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:39.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,バカッ　バカ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:41.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,そうやって　嬉しそうにしちゃ\Nダメだって！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:44.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前が天気変えちまうから\Nばれるんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:48.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルトが怒った。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:51.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,もぉ～　バカヨタ！\Nあっちいけ　あっち。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:54.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,（キバ）きゅうじゅうはち\Nきゅうじゅうきゅう→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:56.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,ひゃ～く！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:04.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルトみっけ！\Nくっそ～　ヨタめ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:11.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,俺を助けるために\N缶を蹴ってくれるヤツなんて→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:13.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,いるのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:22.14,japanese,,0,0,0,,うっ　おわっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:29.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,シカマル　チョウジ　いの　赤丸　で　サクラ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:33.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,あとは　ヨタか。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:37.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:53.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタが泣いてる！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:03.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:07.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:14.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,あの者は　我らが預かる。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:17.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,厳重な監視のもと\N取り調べを行う。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:20.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,ちょっと！　ヨタは　そんなんじゃ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:22.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉の里以外の者が→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:25.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,許可なく里周辺に\N存在することは　許されない。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:27.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,いずれ\Nキミたちにも出頭してもらう。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:30.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,それまで\N自宅で待機しているように。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:33.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヨタは　ヨタは　俺の…))
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:48.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,《あれが　俺たちとヨタとの\N別れの始まりだった》
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:58.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,《そして\N俺たちは　ヨタを死なせた》
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:45.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,＜旬の魚が大好きな豆助＞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.06,0:22:57.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,豆助　きょうのお魚は\N今が旬のあれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.37,0:22:59.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,＜　その魚とは…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:09.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,＜　それは鰹に勝るとも劣らない\N味を持つことから→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:34.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Sad Sun Shower{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.03,0:01:46.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Forehead, forehead, forehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:50.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! Don't make fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:56.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:01:59.36,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:02.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Kon kon kon. It's snowing, kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.90,0:02:05.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yota seems to like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:07.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Your forehead, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:08.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:11.82,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you… What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:16.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Kon kon kon! Kon kon kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.98,0:02:19.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Kon kon kon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.32,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:55.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to give him flowers\NI put together from our shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:58.69,english,,0000,0000,0000,,but Sasuke just ignored me\Nand left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:05.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So sad. Poor Ino. Poor Ino.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.86,0:03:06.82,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yota…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:09.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nice,\Nso I'll give you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:14.11,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ino is so bold…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.69,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to behave that way with Sasuke…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:19.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you having fun, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:20.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:23.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If Sakura is having fun,\NYota is happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:25.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura… Happy about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:27.86,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… It's nothing, Ino.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:36.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yota is so fickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.32,english,,0000,0000,0000,,When he's sad, it rains…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:40.69,english,,0000,0000,0000,,When he's happy, it snows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:44.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:46.82,english,,0000,0000,0000,,WEATHER FOR SALE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:06.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Those flowers…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:07.69,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Yota come…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.11,english,,0000,0000,0000,,To the village…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't do that, Yota.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:18.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to be\Na secret from the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:21.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're discovered,\Nthere's gonna be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:23.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No one saw you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:26.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, no one saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:27.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:31.19,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one…weird kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:32.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:37.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the only one\Noutside during lunch…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:38.82,english,,0000,0000,0000,,sitting on the metal pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.19,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Metal pole?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:41.65,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:49.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:51.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know which one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always alone\Nand looks angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:08.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? He sorta smiles at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:09.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:11.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he likes you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.07,0:05:13.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:15.86,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Naruto notice you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:17.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:19.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Yota.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:23.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go into the village\Never again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:27.94,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're discovered,\Nwe might have to part ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.69,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:32.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be apart from Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:33.94,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:35.69,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yota.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that funny though?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:40.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke who always acts so cool…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.11,english,,0000,0000,0000,,looked like a flower garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:21.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So does this mean\Nwe have to fight Yota?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:25.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the time with Asuma.\NIn order to seal him…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:28.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,we have to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.94,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:33.19,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we beat Yota's weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:34.82,english,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:39.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:42.86,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We don't know anything about Yota.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:45.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can we…?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:48.82,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.19,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Connect me with Sakura!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:51.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:52.65,english,,0000,0000,0000,,All right…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:56.32,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:58.82,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sakura, can you hear me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:00.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ino?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:02.32,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, I'm in the middle{\i0}\N{\i1}of something right now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you remember?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:06.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:07.86,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About Yota!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, I'm…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.36,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}facing that Yota right now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:15.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:24.86,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Over here too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:28.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yota's really mad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:29.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:36.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How come Yota's by you guys too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:38.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Three Yotas?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:57.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Whistling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:15.86,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are…you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:20.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:27.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:34.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're…Yota?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:36.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Yota?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:43.32,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:44.94,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:56.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yota…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:04.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:11.94,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:15.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where'd you put Yota?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:18.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Interrogating him won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:21.19,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, you know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:22.82,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:26.32,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Well… You saw something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:29.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't see him? That…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:32.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't see him,\Nhow could I have seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:32.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:34.94,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty shrewd, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:39.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys so impressed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:41.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:42.65,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you put Yota?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:53.69,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yota?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:57.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You met him in the Academy schoolyard\Nthe other day, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:01.94,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who knows Yota\Nbesides us is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:17.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You met Yota, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:19.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You told everyone, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.23,0:10:21.69,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Yota?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:24.36,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a lost kid near the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:27.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We felt sorry for him,\Nso we took care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But when we came here today,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:32.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,everything was a mess\Nand Yota was gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:36.36,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he's an outsider?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:37.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you protect an outsider,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,but still look at me\Nwith those eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:46.94,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What a thing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:51.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:57.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we questioned him too hard\Nwhen we don't even have proof…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:01.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If he really doesn't know anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:13.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it always me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:21.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lost…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:39.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:58.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:04.24,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:07.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:12.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:15.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:17.74,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:20.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yota!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:20.74,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Yota, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:34.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sun showers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:38.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this…your jutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:40.24,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:43.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I can't even do Clone Jutsu\Nor Transformation Jutsu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:47.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and Iruka Sensei is\Nalways scolding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:52.41,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an outsider,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:54.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,but everyone likes you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:57.41,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet when it comes to me…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:12:58.62,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:00.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.87,0:13:04.16,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You were doing…fuu fuu fuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:04.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:08.62,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You were sitting on the metal pole\Nthe other day and whistling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:10.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:42.16,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me how.\NI want to whistle too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:42.66,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:46.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,When you whistled,\Nyou weren't alone…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:47.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You cheered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:49.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:53.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I was pretending…by whistling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:56.24,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll try pretending too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:58.62,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you have everyone…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.16,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:28.24,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:29.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,how to whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:31.41,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:40.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:42.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,First, you just blow\Nwithout pursing your lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:44.74,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then slowly pucker up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:47.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Make wind sounds… Like "fuuu"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:58.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's…happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:01.99,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So his happiness turns into wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:07.12,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Say…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:11.66,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:16.99,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Fr-i-e-nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:22.74,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:40.41,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there he is! That kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:43.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:47.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:54.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat, not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.95,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to Yota,\Nyou guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.32,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:07.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I was walking Akamaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:09.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:13.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then thunder started\Nrumbling everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17